        <content><![CDATA[<p>Once the network share access has been <a href="%(link0)">set up</a>, network shares can be accessed via the path syntax <code>\\HOSTNAME\SHARENAME</code> (standard Windows syntax) or <code>smb://HOSTNAME/SHARENAME</code> (most other clients).</p>
<div class="alert alert-info">When using one of the&nbsp;<a href="%(link1)">provided share configurations</a> on your local OpenCms installation, the network share is available at <code>\\localhost\OPENCMS</code> (or <code>smb://localhost/OPENCMS</code>).</div>]]></content>
